     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d054n2-ptr" id="PJA08d054n2">2</a>
      <p>That is, the <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Bonhomme Richard.</span></p>
     </div>
